### ×©×œ×‘ 1: Create Your Plugin Class

```python
class MyCustomPlugin:
    """Your custom plugin"""
    
    def __init__(self):
        self.name = "my_plugin"
        self.version = "1.0"
        self.enabled = True
    
    def execute(self, data):
        """Main execution method"""
        # Your code here
        result = process_data(data)
        return {
            "status": "success",
            "result": result,
            "plugin": self.name
        }
```

### ×©×œ×‘ 2: Add to hai_emet_python_backend.py

```python
# In the __main__ section, add:

# Register your plugins
PLUGIN_SYSTEM.register_plugin("my_plugin", MyCustomPlugin)
PLUGIN_SYSTEM.register_plugin("another_plugin", AnotherPlugin)
```

### ×©×œ×‘ 3: Use in Chat Endpoint

```python
@app.route('/chat', methods=['POST'])
def chat():
    # ... existing code ...
    
    # Execute plugin if needed
    plugin_result = GAS_ENGINE.plugins.execute_plugin("my_plugin", {
        "message": message,
        "user_id": user_id,
        "language": language
    })
    
    if plugin_result:
        # Use plugin result
        reply = plugin_result.get("result")
    
    # ... rest of code ...
```

