## ğŸš€ To Add Your Plugin:

1. Create file: `plugins/your_plugin.py`
2. Define class with `execute()` method
3. In main file:
   ```python
   from plugins.your_plugin import YourPlugin
   PLUGIN_SYSTEM.register_plugin("your_plugin", YourPlugin)
   ```
4. Call in chat endpoint when needed
